1. *Mladić* je trčao pored reke. (The young man was running by the river.)
2. Žena je videla *mladića* kako kupuje cveće. (The woman saw a young man buying flowers.)
3. *Mladiću*, da li si video moj telefon? (Young man, have you seen my phone?)
4. Oni su pronašli izgubljenog *mladića* u šumi. (They found a lost young man in the woods.)
5. *Mladićima* se sviđaju moderne tehnologije. (Young men like modern technologies.)
6. *Mladićem* je ovladao osećaj tuge nakon smrti oca. (A young man was overcome with sadness after his father's death.)
7. Videla sam kako *mladić* pomera stolice. (I saw a young man moving chairs.)
8. *Mladiću* je potrebna nova knjiga za učenje engleskog jezika. (The young man needs a new book for learning English.)